{"tid":1388560,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［討論］全民勇武，制服警犬有冇得諗？","createTime":"2019-07-30T17:22:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T14:40:49.000Z","uid":245602,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e66ef49c98202de485af940bc6146e040f4741bc","tid":1388560,"uid":245602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:22:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">利申:唔係鼓吹要暴力咁打死佢地</span><br />\n<br />\n警犬既武力不斷升級<br />\n到今日竟然眾目睽睽之下攞槍對住市民<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SEnEWNi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSEnEWNi.png&h=37ab84b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iA94osj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiA94osj.png&h=d369ac14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢哋愈來愈冇性，實在唔想見到有人再受傷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>因此</strong></span>，當狗衝向人群，有落單機會時，有冇可能可以學d狗咁，組織前線捉住某幾個落單既狗，將佢地制服？例如用索帶綁手綁腳，拖埋一二邊遠離人群<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>切記切記</strong></span>一定要係<span style=\"color: red;\">制服</span>，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係暴打</span></span><br />\n唔可以同班狗一樣，亦唔可以被人捉痛腳，只用適當武力，以武制暴，目標只係為左唔好令手足受傷<br />\n<br />\n雖然危險性高 ，但有幾個優勢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1.人數<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(全民勇武下)</span>我地佔優，可以幾個一齊制服一隻<br />\n2.可以減少當刻狗隻數目，減少手足受傷<br />\n3.可以搶到gear(尤其盾)</span><br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以一齊討論可行性，利弊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0c2882ce9e49a192d77b2aaabe716871fe4ee8","tid":1388560,"uid":245602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:24:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">第一出文，屌細細少少&hellip;</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">出文真心只想手足安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"9d283bfcef726144441f34a874c8b36b6cafb730","tid":1388560,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:29:39.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DErY1NGl2p_M&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=bb99a421\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=ebb414ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong! <br />\nThe Revolution Of Our Times! </span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>五大訴求</strong></span></span></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>Hongkongers 5 Demands:</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n1. Full Withdrawal of the Extradition Bill<br />\n2. Retraction of the Characterisation of the Protestas a Riot<br />\n3. Release all Arrested Protesters<br />\n4. Accountability for Police and Yuen Long White Shirts Brutality<br />\n5. Implement Dual Universal Suffrage"},{"pid":"db55e41ee3e0a1292d92d263c5acb69440a233c5","tid":1388560,"uid":7358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:30:52.000Z","msg":"制服中途暴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07661c2c27d59b33b573a4ef415e4782658d7b13","tid":1388560,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:34:26.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"28a98080dd34ef59d20ebbf5013561c983a8ed91","tid":1388560,"uid":3571,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:41:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"950e9946bc7843450196a12d94b964a8e50745df","tid":1388560,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:43:38.000Z","msg":"警犬父母車頭相<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1388514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1388514</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2acaa111e4c78f59acbe32a2e492dd9a8b00ce73","tid":1388560,"uid":290699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:39:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8a19cada60c9de017f77df826f8861d2637f77fd","tid":1388560,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:44:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f7444b913733bd54a99a6754877c14e1961d54cf","tid":1388560,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9209e04972a3c609df1ea9e125bfe5efa5cf934b","tid":1388560,"uid":285413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e66ef49c98202de485af940bc6146e040f4741bc","tid":1388560,"uid":245602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:22:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">利申:唔係鼓吹要暴力咁打死佢地</span><br />\n<br />\n警犬既武力不斷升級<br />\n到今日竟然眾目睽睽之下攞槍對住市民<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SEnEWNi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSEnEWNi.png&h=37ab84b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iA94osj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiA94osj.png&h=d369ac14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢哋愈來愈冇性，實在唔想見到有人再受傷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>因此</strong></span>，當狗衝向人群，有落單機會時，有冇可能可以學d狗咁，組織前線捉住某幾個落單既狗，將佢地制服？例如用索帶綁手綁腳，拖埋一二邊遠離人群<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>切記切記</strong></span>一定要係<span style=\"color: red;\">制服</span>，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係暴打</span></span><br />\n唔可以同班狗一樣，亦唔可以被人捉痛腳，只用適當武力，以武制暴，目標只係為左唔好令手足受傷<br />\n<br />\n雖然危險性高 ，但有幾個優勢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1.人數<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(全民勇武下)</span>我地佔優，可以幾個一齊制服一隻<br />\n2.可以減少當刻狗隻數目，減少手足受傷<br />\n3.可以搶到gear(尤其盾)</span><br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以一齊討論可行性，利弊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:21:48.000Z","msg":"可見，連登人已被「仇恨支配自己」，勇武是大多數，出post問有冇可能拉攏警方，畀人diu到飛起; <br />\n出post問用武力制服警方，大家支持，<br />\n可見風向。<br />\n<br />\n中共樂見，我哋累鬥累，<br />\n佢就坐享漁人之利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>畀2個points你思考吓啦:<br />\n1.人數冇錯係我哋贏，但佢哋有槍有炮有武器喎，哩啲火器嘅發明就係令戰爭不用再鬥人多而發明的<br />\n2.冇錯，而家香港係冇咗法治，咁你想唔想佢有返先?咁你大義凜然地話「以武制暴」時，你日後是否願意承擔一切法律責任與後果先?<br />\n</strong><br />\n我就係諗極武力搞唔掂先諗用軟功，點知畀人喪diu<br />\n#忠言逆耳"},{"pid":"22545122227e40894f3ef6e0ab12895a12e8500d","tid":1388560,"uid":245602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9209e04972a3c609df1ea9e125bfe5efa5cf934b","tid":1388560,"uid":285413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e66ef49c98202de485af940bc6146e040f4741bc","tid":1388560,"uid":245602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:22:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">利申:唔係鼓吹要暴力咁打死佢地</span><br />\n<br />\n警犬既武力不斷升級<br />\n到今日竟然眾目睽睽之下攞槍對住市民<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SEnEWNi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSEnEWNi.png&h=37ab84b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iA94osj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiA94osj.png&h=d369ac14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢哋愈來愈冇性，實在唔想見到有人再受傷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>因此</strong></span>，當狗衝向人群，有落單機會時，有冇可能可以學d狗咁，組織前線捉住某幾個落單既狗，將佢地制服？例如用索帶綁手綁腳，拖埋一二邊遠離人群<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>切記切記</strong></span>一定要係<span style=\"color: red;\">制服</span>，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係暴打</span></span><br />\n唔可以同班狗一樣，亦唔可以被人捉痛腳，只用適當武力，以武制暴，目標只係為左唔好令手足受傷<br />\n<br />\n雖然危險性高 ，但有幾個優勢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1.人數<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(全民勇武下)</span>我地佔優，可以幾個一齊制服一隻<br />\n2.可以減少當刻狗隻數目，減少手足受傷<br />\n3.可以搶到gear(尤其盾)</span><br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以一齊討論可行性，利弊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:21:48.000Z","msg":"可見，連登人已被「仇恨支配自己」，勇武是大多數，出post問有冇可能拉攏警方，畀人diu到飛起; <br />\n出post問用武力制服警方，大家支持，<br />\n可見風向。<br />\n<br />\n中共樂見，我哋累鬥累，<br />\n佢就坐享漁人之利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>畀2個points你思考吓啦:<br />\n1.人數冇錯係我哋贏，但佢哋有槍有炮有武器喎，哩啲火器嘅發明就係令戰爭不用再鬥人多而發明的<br />\n2.冇錯，而家香港係冇咗法治，咁你想唔想佢有返先?咁你大義凜然地話「以武制暴」時，你日後是否願意承擔一切法律責任與後果先?<br />\n</strong><br />\n我就係諗極武力搞唔掂先諗用軟功，點知畀人喪diu<br />\n#忠言逆耳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:11:07.000Z","msg":"淨係武力當然唔會搞得掂，所以軟功有不斷升級，增加密度，威力(全港不合作運動-罷工）<br />\n不過政府只在武力方面升級，唔肯正面回應，所以我先覺得武力方面都不能坐而待斃，保護返集會遊行活動，互相配合<br />\n<br />\n關於你2個pt,其實正係現況<br />\n1.武力佢地佔上風，所以我呢個方法只能博佢地唔敢出到最高武力，仍需討論<br />\n2.已經有182人被捕，49人被控，我唔會怕同佢地承擔"},{"pid":"250e782d52e10d0aaba8caa4d2b3475f143744a1","tid":1388560,"uid":245602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:13:09.000Z","msg":"拉攏警方其實都得，但機會好微"},{"pid":"f510a2a9ce132b27f72019ff5db3e0888d527c36","tid":1388560,"uid":245602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:17:59.000Z","msg":"仲有<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">再次強調，唔係無目的地暴力，係制服</span><br />\n壓落地不致命為前提，要show到我地理性一面"},{"pid":"c929d40fa9b7343557e60c8e782b7d3fef063cf9","tid":1388560,"uid":155253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:19:20.000Z","msg":"武裝解除<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最好制服都除埋"},{"pid":"1f711560046c7cc1dea1c8475735a06d4e5e0a6c","tid":1388560,"uid":263485,"like":0,